<%
  heading ||= "Treine com quem entende do seu objetivo."
  subheading ||= "Conecte-se a profissionais de educação física e transforme sua rotina com mentorias personalizadas."
%>
<aside class="relative hidden lg:flex lg:w-1/2 bg-gradient-primary text-primary-foreground overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-white/30 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-[28rem] w-[28rem] rounded-full bg-white/20 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col justify-between w-full px-12 py-14">
    <%= link_to root_path, class: "inline-flex items-center gap-3 group" do %>
      <span class="inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white/15 backdrop-blur ring-1 ring-white/30 shadow-elevated transition-smooth group-hover:scale-105">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6">
          <path d="M14.4 14.4 9.6 9.6"/>
          <path d="M18.657 21.485a2 2 0 1 1-2.829-2.828l-1.767 1.768a2 2 0 1 1-2.829-2.829l6.364-6.364a2 2 0 1 1 2.829 2.829l-1.768 1.767a2 2 0 1 1 2.828 2.829z"/>
          <path d="m21.5 21.5-1.4-1.4"/>
          <path d="M3.9 3.9 2.5 2.5"/>
          <path d="M6.404 12.768a2 2 0 1 1-2.829-2.829l1.768-1.767a2 2 0 1 1-2.828-2.829l2.828-2.828a2 2 0 1 1 2.829 2.828l1.767-1.768a2 2 0 1 1 2.829 2.829z"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <span class="text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">
        Fit<span class="text-white/90">Mentor</span>
      </span>
    <% end %>

    <div class="space-y-6 max-w-md">
      <h1 class="text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-[1.05]">
        <%= heading %>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base xl:text-lg text-primary-foreground/85 leading-relaxed">
        <%= subheading %>
      </p>

      <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-primary-foreground/90">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/20 ring-1 ring-white/40">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-3 w-3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
          </span>
          Mentores verificados e especializados.
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/20 ring-1 ring-white/40">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-3 w-3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
          </span>
          Sessões agendadas em poucos cliques.
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/20 ring-1 ring-white/40">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-3 w-3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
          </span>
          Acompanhamento contínuo da sua evolução.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p class="text-xs text-primary-foreground/70">
      © <%= Date.current.year %> FitMentor · Todos os direitos reservados.
    </p>
  </div>
</aside>
